ht have a transparent background, making the gap visible.\n\nBut wait, the user said \"not using the full width of the available column width\" \u2014 this sounds like a significant gap, not just 1 pixel.\n\nLet me take one more look. Maybe the problem is specifically about the `_columns_layout.invalidate()` call at the end of `show_all_columns`. This invalidates the HBox layout, which could trigger a relayout that changes the splitter width:",
